ubleshooting JavaScript involves understanding the types of errors, using debugging tools, and applying logical thinking to fix issues. Always start with syntax errors, move on to runtime errors, and finally tackle logical errors. Regular practice and familiarizing yourself with common mistakes will improve your debugging skills.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">Happy coding and debugging!</p></h4>',"https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=1000,height=420,fit=cover,gravity=auto,format=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fehtj080ljdcd5eq217h6.png", 'published', (SELECT id FROM categories WHERE name = 'JavaScript'), TRUE, 400, '2024-01-01 08:00:00', (SELECT id FROM users WHERE name = 'Bob Smith')),
 (15, 'Typescript: Interface', 'JIn this article, you''ll learn about what interface are and how to use them, along with the difference between type and interface. This article gives you a basic understanding of the interface.', 
    '<p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">In this article, you''ll learn about what&nbsp;interface are and how to use them, along with the difference between type&nbsp;and&nbsp;interface. This article gives you a basic understanding of the interface.</p><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; border-left: 4px solid var(--base-20); padding: 0 0 0 var(--content-rhythm); color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0;">This is going to be a full series of typescript where you will learn from basic topics like string, boolean to more complex like Type Aliases, enums, Interface, generics, and etc.</p></blockquote><h3 style="margin: calc(var(--content-rhythm) / 2) 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: var(--fw-bold); line-height: var(--lh-tight); font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;"><a name="table-of-contents" href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#table-of-contents" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;"></a>Table of Contents</h3><ul style="padding-left: var(--su-6); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><li><a href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#interface" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;">Interface</a></li><li><a href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#interface-vs-type" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;">Interface vs Type</a><ul style="padding-left: var(--su-6); margin: 0 0 0 var(--content-rhythm); list-style-type: square;"><li><a href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#adding-new-fields" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;">Adding new fields</a></li><li><a href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#extends" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;">Extends</a></li><li><a href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#union" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;">Union</a></li></ul></li></ul><h2 style="margin: calc(var(--content-rhythm) / 2) 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: var(--fw-bold); line-height: var(--lh-tight); font-size: 1.5em; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;"><a name="interface" href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#interface" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;"></a>Interface</h2><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">An&nbsp;<em>interface declaration</em>&nbsp;is another way to name an object type. You can create it by using the&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">interface</code>&nbsp;keyword:<br></p><div class="highlight js-code-highlight" style="background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); font-size: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; overflow-x: auto; overflow-wrap: initial; padding: var(--su-6); position: relative; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><pre class="highlight typescript" style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 1em; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color);"><code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%;"><span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">interface</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="nl" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">name</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>
    <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">age</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">number</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>

<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// ✅ CORRECT</span>
<span class="kd" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">let</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">newUser</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span><span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">name</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">John</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span> <span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">age</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="mi" style="color: var(--syntax-literal-color);">28</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">};</span>
<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// ❌ ERROR: property ''age'' is missing</span>
<span class="kd" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">let</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">newUser</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span><span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">name</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">John</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">};</span>
<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// ❌ ERROR: missing the following properties from type ''User'': name, age </span>
<span class="kd" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">let</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">newUser</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{};</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight__panel js-actions-panel" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; display: flex; visibility: hidden;"><div class="highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action" style="display: flex; padding: var(--su-2); overflow: hidden; background: var(--base-60); border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius); opacity: 0.9;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on"><path d="M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">You can also use&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">readonly</code>&nbsp;and optional approach in&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">interface</code>:<br></p><div class="highlight js-code-highlight" style="background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); font-size: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; overflow-x: auto; overflow-wrap: initial; padding: var(--su-6); position: relative; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><pre class="highlight typescript" style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 1em; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color);"><code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%;"><span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">interface</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="k" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">readonly</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">id</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">number</span>     <span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// readonly variable</span>
    <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">name</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>
    <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">age</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">number</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>
    <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">specialKey</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">?</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>   <span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// optional </span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight__panel js-actions-panel" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; display: flex; visibility: hidden;"><div class="highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action" style="display: flex; padding: var(--su-2); overflow: hidden; background: var(--base-60); border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius); opacity: 0.9;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on"><path d="M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">You can also pass functions to the&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">interface</code>, there are two ways to do that:<br></p><div class="highlight js-code-highlight" style="background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); font-size: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; overflow-x: auto; overflow-wrap: initial; padding: var(--su-6); position: relative; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><pre class="highlight typescript" style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 1em; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color);"><code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%;"><span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// Method-1</span>
<span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">interface</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="nf" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">getDiscount</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">(</span><span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">coupon</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">):</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">number</span>     
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>

<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// For Both you need to call this like this:</span>
<span class="kd" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">const</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">newUser</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">getDiscount</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">(</span><span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">coupon</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">KIJ298DD9J</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">)</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=&gt;</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
        <span class="k" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">return</span> <span class="mi" style="color: var(--syntax-literal-color);">10</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">;</span>
    <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>

<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// Method-2</span>
<span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">interface</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="nl" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">getDiscount</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">(</span><span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">coupon</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">)</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=&gt;</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">number</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>

<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// 👉 You see I have changed the ''coupon'' to ''couponName''</span>
<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// You don''t need to match the name of the parameter here</span>
<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// It will take care of it</span>
<span class="kd" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">const</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">newUser</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">getDiscount</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">(</span><span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">couponName</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">KIJ298DD9J</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">)</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=&gt;</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
        <span class="k" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">return</span> <span class="mi" style="color: var(--syntax-literal-color);">10</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">;</span>
    <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight__panel js-actions-panel" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; display: flex; visibility: hidden;"><div class="highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action" style="display: flex; padding: var(--su-2); overflow: hidden; background: var(--base-60); border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius); opacity: 0.9;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on"><path d="M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">In&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;">Method 1</span>&nbsp;you can simply use the&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">()</code>&nbsp;to say it functions like:&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">getDiscount(): number</code>&nbsp;and string are the return types, and it takes no arguments.</p><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">In&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;">Method 2</span>&nbsp;we use an arrow function like&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">getDiscount: () =&gt; number</code>.</p><h2 style="margin: calc(var(--content-rhythm) / 2) 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: var(--fw-bold); line-height: var(--lh-tight); font-size: 1.5em; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;"><a name="interface-vs-type" href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#interface-vs-type" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;"></a>Interface vs Type</h2><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">Type aliases and interfaces are very similar, and in many cases, you can choose between them freely. Almost all features of an&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">interface</code>&nbsp;are available in&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">type</code>&nbsp;The key distinction is that a type cannot be reopened to add new properties vs. an interface that is always extendable.</p><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">Let’s Differentiate them with a few examples:</p><h3 style="margin: calc(var(--content-rhythm) / 2) 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: var(--fw-bold); line-height: var(--lh-tight); font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;"><a name="adding-new-fields" href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#adding-new-fields" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;"></a>Adding new fields</h3><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">In&nbsp;<code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: var(--code-inline-bg); color: var(--color-body-color); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%; padding: 0.1em 0.25em;">interface</code>&nbsp;you can add new fields to the existing interface, but you cannot add new fields to an existing type. It will throw an error.</p><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Interface</span><br></p><div class="highlight js-code-highlight" style="background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); font-size: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; overflow-x: auto; overflow-wrap: initial; padding: var(--su-6); position: relative; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><pre class="highlight typescript" style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 1em; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color);"><code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%;"><span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">interface</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="nl" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">id</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">;</span>    
    <span class="nl" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">email</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">;</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>

<span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">interface</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="nl" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">name</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="kr" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">string</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">;</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>

<span class="c1" style="color: var(--syntax-comment-color);">// Now you can add all the three values to the User interface</span>
<span class="kd" style="color: var(--syntax-declaration-color);">const</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">user</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="nx" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">User</span> <span class="o" style="color: var(--syntax-error-color);">=</span> <span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">{</span>
    <span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">id</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">2323232</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>
    <span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">email</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">foo@email.com</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">,</span>
    <span class="na" style="color: var(--syntax-name-color);">name</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">:</span> <span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="s2" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">Foo</span><span class="dl" style="color: var(--syntax-string-color);">"</span><span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">;</span>
<span class="p" style="color: var(--syntax-text-color);">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight__panel js-actions-panel" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; display: flex; visibility: hidden;"><div class="highlight__panel-action js-fullscreen-code-action" style="display: flex; padding: var(--su-2); overflow: hidden; background: var(--base-60); border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius); opacity: 0.9;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="highlight-action crayons-icon highlight-action--fullscreen-on"><path d="M16 3h6v6h-2V5h-4V3zM2 3h6v2H4v4H2V3zm18 16v-4h2v6h-6v-2h4zM4 19h4v2H2v-6h2v4z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Type</span><br></p><div class="highlight js-code-highlight" style="background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color); font-size: 16px; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; overflow-x: auto; overflow-wrap: initial; padding: var(--su-6); position: relative; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><pre class="highlight typescript" style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 1em; background: var(--syntax-background-color); color: var(--syntax-text-color);"><code style="font-family: var(--ff-monospace); font-size: 16px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius); max-width: 100%;"><span class=